These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, american, japanese, pakistani
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, chinchilla, mouse, goat
1. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8
2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the thai##1
3. the american is on the left or right of the japanese##3
4. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
5. the pakistani is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
6. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the american##5
7. the american is somewhere between the thai and the owner of the chinchilla##7
8. the american and the owner of the goat have the same parity positions##9
9. the japanese and the owner of the goldfish have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | thai | american | japanese     | pakistani |
| Pet           | mouse   | goat     | chinchilla | goldfish  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, mirinda, lemonade
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, puzzles, baking, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is card-games and the person drinking soy-milk have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##8
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
6. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
7. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | lemonade     | mirinda    | water | soy-milk    |
| Hobby      | video-games | puzzles | baking      | card-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, 7up, iced-tea
There 4 different types of food: corn, pineapple, cabbage, blueberry
1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person eating cabbage##5
2. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating corn##1
7. the person eating corn is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
8. the person drinking tea and the person eating pineapple have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | tea    | 7up   | sprite    | iced-tea  |
| Food       | pineapple | blueberry | corn | cabbage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, electrician, journalist, nurse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, techno, rock, country
1. the fan disco is the electrician##1
2. the fan techno is on the right of the fan rock##1
3. the fan techno is somewhere to the left of the electrician##5
4. the fan country is on the left or right of the journalist##3
5. the fan techno is on the left of the freelancer##1
6. the nurse and the fan country have the same parity positions##9
7. the journalist is on the left or right of the freelancer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | nurse | journalist | freelancer  | electrician |
| Music-Genre   | rock             | techno          | country | disco    |

