.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, gospel, rock, ambient
4 different pets are kept: rat, goat, mouse, hamster
1. the fan rock is not the owner of the mouse##6
2. the owner of the rat and the fan indie have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the goat and the fan gospel have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the fan rock##5
5. the owner of the rat is on the left of the fan ambient##1
6. the fan gospel is not the owner of the goat##6
7. the fan ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan gospel##5
8. the owner of the rat is on the right of the fan indie##1
9. the owner of the hamster is not the fan ambient##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | indie | rock | ambient  | gospel |
| Pet           | goat   | rat     | mouse | hamster      |

