2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
4. the mexican and the person watching thriller movies have the same parity positions##9
5. the person watching family movies and the mexican have different parity positions##9
6. the canadian is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
7. the russian is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
8. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the russian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | satire | thriller | family |
| Nationality   | russian        | canadian    | mexican   | french |

