2. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's sport is rugby##2
3. the person who's sport is water-polo and the fan rock have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the fan rock is not to the right of the fan folk##8
6. the fan soul is somewhere to the left of the fan folk##5
7. the fan rock is somewhere to the right of the fan trance##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | soul | rock         | folk     |
| Sport         | snowboarding | water-polo  | rugby | basketball |

