4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the owner of the cat##6
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
7. the person who's hobby is photography and the owner of the turtle have the same parity positions##9

