.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, apricot, pear, radish
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, helicopter, skateboard, train
1. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person eating onion##8
2. the person eating radish and the person driving the train have the same parity positions##9
3. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
4. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
5. the person eating apricot is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the train##7
6. the person eating radish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | pear | onion   | apricot | radish |
| Transport   | skateboard   | helicopter | ship    | train      |

