.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, pomegranate, carrot, raspberry
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, french, thai, indonesian
1. the person eating raspberry is not the indonesian##6
2. the indonesian is not to the right of the dutch##8
3. the person eating carrot is not to the left of the person eating raspberry##8
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the thai##3
6. the indonesian is on the far left##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
8. the person eating lettuce is the french##1
9. the person eating raspberry and the dutch have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | pomegranate   | raspberry    | carrot | lettuce    |
| Nationality   | indonesian | dutch | thai   | french |

