.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, lemonade, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, documentary, scientific, zombie
1. the person watching satire movies is not the person drinking water##6
2. the person drinking water is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
8. the person watching satire movies and the person drinking 7up have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching scientific movies and the person drinking lemonade have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | water   | coffee  | lemonade  | 7up |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | scientific | zombie | satire      |

