.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee, iced-tea, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, gospel, folk, disco
 1. the person drinking coffee and the fan folk have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 3. the fan rock is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking soy-milk##7
 4. the fan folk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan folk is not to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 7. the person drinking almond-milk and the fan gospel have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the fan disco##3
 9. the fan disco is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the fan rock##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk  | almond-milk | iced-tea  | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | disco | folk     | rock | gospel     |

