2. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person drinking juice and the person who's hobby is chess have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
