.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea, fanta, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, sudoku, writing, video-games
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##8
 4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##8
 7. the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is sudoku have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is sudoku have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | fanta        | soy-milk   | hot-chocolate      |
| Hobby      | video-games | writing | sudoku | rock-climbing |

 